qualitative_feedback: Giving a score of 1 to 10 was the most difficult as it was hard to be fair and determine what I thought deserved a certain number. Choosing the 5 best arguments was fairly easy as I didn't really need to rank the statements. Dragging to rank all the choices was somewhat difficult but visually it was simple and easy because I was able to see my choices in order, rather than just attributing them a number 1 through 10.
